elser for menighetene.", "- I andre saker har det vist seg at det asylantene trengte var \u00e5 f\u00e5 ro i en kaotisk situasjon, sier hun.", "Biskop sterkt kritisk til \u00e5 endre kirkeasyl-instruks"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "fcf101b92e56e372acff1a17fc81b2d9f78927bd0b2ca70513daac5b2ab4c445"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T12:27:11.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Kirkeasyl kan v\u00e6re den eneste m\u00e5ten \u00e5 f\u00e5 myndighetene til \u00e5 se p\u00e5 en sak p\u00e5 nytt, og det har resultert i opphold, sier tidligere pastor Arnfinn Aandal."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12086117.ece/m7d83j/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Arnfinn%20Aandal.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8faa89830e256c35f8c24292ecc74bfa91ab144b.jpg?593c1067"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Kirkeasyl er ingen lystbetont aff\u00e6re -adressa.no", "- Uh\u00f8rt", "Ni \u00e5r i kirkeasyl", "Ikke naiv", "Tenker p\u00e5 Maria", "\u00c5pen kirke", "Vern i kirkerommet"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "8faa89830e256c35f8c24292ecc74bfa91ab144b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["asyls\u00f8kere", "asylmottak", "Politikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "asyls\u00f8kere,asylmottak,Politikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kirke", "kirkeasyl", "levende mennesker", "\u00e5pen kirke", "t\u00f8nne salt", "lystbetont aff\u00e6re"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["politikk", "kalvskinnet", "jesus", "storskog", "nidaros", "politisk", "baptistkirken", "vern", "krf", "bibelen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value":